@@TJvSelectDirectory
<TITLEIMG TJvSelectDirectory>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.Dialogs.Common>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Displays a directory-selection dialog.
Description
  The TJvSelectDirectory component is a wrapper for the two SelectDirectory functions. It displays a
  modal dialog box for selecting a directory. The dialog does not appear at runtime until it is
  activated by a call to the Execute method.
  
  Use property ClassicDialog to specify whether to show the Windows directory browser or the classic
  Select \Directory dialog box.

